results.name: Permutation of natural numbers: a(n) = A246262(A064216((2*n)-1)).
comment: This permutation is induced when A064216 is restricted to odd numbers (equally, when A064989 is restricted to the numbers of form 4k+1) and the resulting numbers are "ranked" with A246262.
